98
00:05:25,802 --> 00:05:27,904
thumbs, and that's the beginning of your interaction.

99
00:05:27,904 --> 00:05:32,027
Something meaningful happens when you move your thumbs on

100
00:05:32,027 --> 00:05:34,209
the button, and whatever is meaningful, it's a feedback

101
00:05:34,209 --> 00:05:35,930
that gets bounced back to you through the screen.

102
00:05:35,930 --> 00:05:38,733
