00:06:39,376 --> 00:06:40,357
and things are happening.

120
00:06:40,357 --> 00:06:44,601
Compared to other type of interactive experiences,

121
00:06:44,601 --> 00:06:47,424
for example, like face-to-face social interactions,

122
00:06:47,424 --> 00:06:49,346
not the kind of social interactions we do on Facebook,

123
00:06:49,346 --> 00:06:50,207
but face-to-face.

124
00:06:51,568 --> 00:06:56,512
It's still an interactive experience. It's still like something interactive that we do with others which is meaningful

125
00:06:56,512 --> 00:07:02,096
But it requires the use of our entire body. I think you know body language for example you can rely on

126
00:07:02,096 --> 00:07:06,479
like entire spectrum of movements that your body allows to actually

127
00:07:06,479 --> 00:07:09,741
to actually like like make meanings with others

