00:08:19,935 --> 00:08:23,216
actually quite fit here because we have like you know the

146
00:08:23,216 --> 00:08:25,637
player moving hands and manipulating handling those

147
00:08:25,637 --> 00:08:26,418
weapons correctly.

148
00:08:27,337 --> 00:08:29,699
So, like, how can we do that?

