00:31:51,743 --> 00:31:52,003
Thanks.

581
00:31:52,003 --> 00:31:56,105
That's how to recap on this.

582
00:31:56,300 --> 00:32:04,307
This, it's been like, we didn't want to have UIs on the camera at the beginning, even though

