604
00:33:16,654 --> 00:33:18,395
because the action can be so frantic,

605
00:33:18,395 --> 00:33:21,436
and you might feel actually so overwhelmed

606
00:33:21,436 --> 00:33:22,657
with everything that happens around you,

607
00:33:22,657 --> 00:33:26,398
which is kind of threatening.

608
00:33:26,398 --> 00:33:29,960
We basically slow down time every time you open

609
00:33:29,960 --> 00:33:34,442
any of those UI for selecting arrows.

