00:33:34,442 --> 00:33:38,283
It was thought out to be a way to help the people

611
00:33:38,283 --> 00:33:40,024
to actually select the arrows properly,

612
00:33:40,024 --> 00:33:42,305
but then it became a trick the players exploited

613
00:33:42,305 --> 00:33:43,706
to actually do better.

614
00:33:44,420 --> 00:33:47,522
you know, the game. So, you know, it turned out in those ways.

