00:33:56,229 --> 00:33:59,192
we knew that we wanted to minimize it as much as possible

619
00:33:59,192 --> 00:34:01,794
and really just make it about like the action.

620
00:34:01,794 --> 00:34:06,157
And in fact, we, like the only kind of like UI augmentation

621
00:34:06,157 --> 00:34:09,760
we did were the one that you see there,

622
00:34:09,760 --> 00:34:13,263
like the health plus, like the selection of the arrows.

623
00:34:13,848 --> 00:34:14,188
Thank you.

