00:36:05,222 --> 00:36:07,104
Yeah, we did.

663
00:36:07,104 --> 00:36:08,907
Mostly, they are the same.

664
00:36:09,547 --> 00:36:12,989
like optic curves, let's call them that way.

665
00:36:12,989 --> 00:36:14,829
Mostly they are the same, but in a few occasions

