00:36:17,110 --> 00:36:19,591
So, because like the vibe is very different.

669
00:36:19,591 --> 00:36:22,012
The Oculus was much better from this point of view.

670
00:36:22,012 --> 00:36:23,512
It like give you a much better response.

671
00:36:23,512 --> 00:36:25,713
Also like in terms of kind of like identifying

672
00:36:25,713 --> 00:36:27,454
a different type of optic, you know,

